<h1>
  Retail Sales Locations
</h1>
<p>
  MBTA riders can purchase fares for the Commuter Rail, Bus, Subway, and Ferry at stores located throughout the Greater Boston and Providence areas.
</p>

<h2>Find a Store Near You</h2>
<h3 class="h5">Enter your location</h3>
<%= form_for @conn, @conn.request_path<>"#address-search-input", [as: :location, method: :get, class: "form"], fn _f -> %>
  <%= input_location(%InputLocation{id: "address-search-input", name: :location, name_index: :address,
                                    address: @address, address_error: get_flash(@conn, :info), submit: true,
                                    required: true, placeholder: "Enter a location", button_class: ""}) %>
<% end %>
<%= unless @fare_sales_locations == [] do %>
  <%= render "_nearby_locations.html", fare_sales_locations: @fare_sales_locations, search_position: @search_position %>
<% end %>
<h2>
  How It Works
</h2>
<h3>
  Bus and Subway
</h3>
<p>
  You can purchase any Bus or Subway pass (1-Day, 7-Day, Monthly) or load up to $100
  for One Way fares at a retail sales location. <%= link "CharlieCards", to: fare_path(@conn, :show, "payment-methods")<>"#charlie-card" %> and
  <%= link "CharlieTickets", to: fare_path(@conn, :show, "payment-methods")<>"#charlie-ticket" %> will be available to you at these locations
  free of charge if you do not already have one.
</p>
<h3>
  Commuter Rail
</h3>
<p>
You can purchase any Commuter Rail pass (One Way, Round Trip, Monthly) at a retail sales location. Your Sales Agent will load your pass onto a
<%= link "CharlieTicket", to: fare_path(@conn, :show, "payment-methods")<>"#charlie-ticket" %>.
</p>
<h3>
  Ferry
</h3>
<p>
You can purchase a Ferry Monthly Pass at retail sales locations. Your Sales Agent will load your pass onto a
<%= link "CharlieTicket", to: fare_path(@conn, :show, "payment-methods")<>"#charlie-ticket" %>.
</p>
<h3>
  Reduced Fares
</h3>
<p>
  If you are eligible for reduced fares and have a <%= link "Senior CharlieCard", to: fare_path(@conn, :show, :reduced)<>"#reduced-senior" %>
  or <%= link "Transportation Access Pass", to: fare_path(@conn, :show, :reduced)<>"#reduced-disability" %>,
  you can purchase new passes or One Way fares at retail sales locations.
  If you have a <%= link "Student CharlieCard", to: fare_path(@conn, :show, :reduced)<>"#students" %>, you may load money onto a
  <%= link "CharlieCard", to: fare_path(@conn, :show, "payment-methods")<>"#charlie-card" %> or
  <%= link "CharlieTicket", to: fare_path(@conn, :show, "payment-methods")<>"#charlie-ticket" %>
  for reduced One Way fares only.
</p>
<h3>
  Purchasing Monthly Passes
</h3>
<p>
  You may purchase a Monthly Pass for the current month though the 14th of that month.
  Monthly passes purchased on the 15th of the month or later will be eligible for use
  during the next calendar month.
</p>
<div class="callout">
  <strong>Monthly Pass on sale now:</strong> <%= @current_pass %>
</div>
<h2>Related Pages</h2>
<div class="title-card-container title-card-container-separate">
  <%= render "_mode_pay.html", mode: :commuter_rail %>
  <%= render "_related_page_card.html", title: "Payment Methods", body: ["Ways to pay your fare", "Where each payment method can be used", "Types of fares you can load onto each payment method"], href: fare_path(@conn, :show, "payment-methods"), target: "_self" %>
  <%= render "_related_page_card.html", title: "Pass Purchase Programs", body: ["Corporations", "Schools and Universities", "Tour and Field Trip groups"], href: redirect_path(@conn, "pass_program"), target: "_blank" %>
  <%= render "_related_page_card.html", title: "Reduced Fares", body: ["Find out if you qualify", "How to get your reduced fares"], href: redirect_path(@conn, "reduced"), target: "_blank" %>
</div>
